{"tid":815131,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S9、Note 9 賣不動","createTime":"2018-09-11T19:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T17:15:39.000Z","uid":109383,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1d198a852cd55ef03324727edf0cdc5d312bc5","tid":815131,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"Galaxy S9、Note 9 賣不動，Strategy Analytics：三星今年銷量恐跌破 3 億支<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/09/10/strategy-analytics-samaung-smart-phone-sale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2Fstrategy-analytics-samaung-smart-phone-sale%2F&d=C0cUpajQUBCSk6CEX00DVC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3253dfe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/09/10/strategy-analytics-samaung-smart-phone-sale/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSA 指出，會預估三星智慧手機銷售量跌破 3 億支，主要是因為旗艦機種 Galaxy S9 和 Note 9 銷售不振，加上受到競爭對手中國廠商急速抬頭的影響。<span style=\"color: red;\">今年 3 月開賣的 S9 銷售不如預期，而 8 月開賣的 Note 9 最終銷售量預估僅 870 萬支。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n在全球前 5 大智慧手機廠中，除三星之外的另 4 大廠今年銷售量皆預估將呈現增長。蘋果預估將年增 1.8% 至 2 億 1,960 萬支、華為將大增 30% 至 1 億 9,940 萬支、小米將大增 40% 至 1 億 2,770 萬支、Oppo 預估將成長 2% 至 1 億 2,030 萬支。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcfc7bb8d93bc1d417f28aaeff7f9eb38d089f7","tid":815131,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T19:24:24.000Z","msg":"YOU ARE FAKE NEWS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4445ac04554bca15bdf88f014aafc653d8157c","tid":815131,"uid":192327,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T19:24:37.000Z","msg":"845 人地間間賤賣"},{"pid":"9343042aebc7cea1bffad49de90c1609dc685123","tid":815131,"uid":35815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T23:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"